OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fbright end to the day but some patchy
OL,7,Flow cloud along the Solway coast. Then
OL,8,Fdry with lengthening clear spells
OL,9,Fovernight. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,12,Fsunshine, but some cloud bubbling up
OL,13,Fin the afternoon. Becoming very warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,16,Fand bright with plenty of sunshine
OL,17,Fduring this period. Very warm in
OL,18,Fgeneral, but cooler at times along the
OL,19,Feast coast.
